data.description:
Truly a WOW End Unit Home. Enjoy nearly 2000sqft of updated 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhome nestled within the highly sought-after Three Fountains community. The generously Vaulted living room Ceilings welcomes you with a fresh ambiance, showcasing new paint that complements the elegant transformation of the fireplace into a pristine white centerpiece. The master bedroom has been tastefully adorned with a neutral color palette, enhancing the overall sense of tranquility. Ascend to the upper level, where a generously sized master bedroom suite awaits, featuring dual closets for your organizational needs.

Secluded at the end of the complex and enveloped by mature trees, this end unit exudes a cozy and private atmosphere. The 2-car attached; oversized garage not only provides convenient parking but also ample storage space for your belongings.

Nearby, enjoy access to the community's pool, clubhouse, and fitness center, perfect for relaxation and social gatherings. The property's prime location ensures proximity to an array of stores, restaurants, and various amenities, offering unparalleled convenience. Commuting is a breeze with quick access to I-25, enhancing the appeal of this residence.

Elevate your lifestyle with this exquisite townhouse – a harmonious blend of contemporary updates, thoughtful design, and an unbeatable location. Schedule your tour today to experience the allure of this move-in-ready gem. Home has been sewer scoped, radon tested, and inspected.
